{"tid":584720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭耀棠：工聯會一直爭取集體談判權　籲政府勿縮沙","createTime":"2018-03-08T04:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T09:04:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cb37aecfb9eeea0a327b71b4c0dafe6c5b2b3292","tid":584720,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"九巴解僱車長風波全城關注。工聯會榮譽會長鄭耀棠昨被問到九巴接連發生勞資爭拗，是否因無立法制訂「集體談判權」，鄭耀棠稱無必然關係，又指工聯會一直爭取「集體談判權」。<br />\n<br />\n1997年臨時立法會通過廢除《集體談判權條例》，當時鄭耀棠投「棄權票」。昨天被問到九巴接連發生勞資爭拗是否「昨日所作的因，種下今天的果」，鄭耀棠指兩者沒必然關係，重申當年審議時間不足。<br />\n<br />\n鄭耀棠又稱，工聯會一直爭取成立中央、行業和企業三層談判機制，惟僱主強烈反對，而無論是殖民地政府或特區政府，對「集體談判權」都相當忌諱。他要求政府勿再「縮沙」，僱主也應持開明態度，訂立「集體談判權」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，當年就《集體談判權條例》投下贊成票、現為勞工及福利局長的羅致光昨日表示，本港情況較複雜，不少公司同時有多個工會，各工會存在競爭，對勞資談判不理想，難達共識。"},{"pid":"1d0bed16cade561ec3e1bcf9c2af762535b68f75","tid":584720,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"嘩，你講野都幾婉轉喎<br />\n工賊會一直爭取集體談判權"},{"pid":"b020c5ba703cc412687d848e052356fd1b4a7675","tid":584720,"uid":49609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"當年審議時間不足就投棄權票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔明嘅嘢你死去改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔好去死??"},{"pid":"117a5b951e9f3830f415fa1841e4f6b0b5c12c77","tid":584720,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"依家先出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bd342e94e37109f53ff509e64bf377e56934db","tid":584720,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b020c5ba703cc412687d848e052356fd1b4a7675","tid":584720,"uid":49609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"當年審議時間不足就投棄權票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔明嘅嘢你死去改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔好去死??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意袋住先 當年又唔袋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9206872e844e1ff5a996ee39bf96a5d6fabd8a20","tid":584720,"uid":8566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"工聯會賣工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0b5c0b5666ca8e60d29882ac57bda66a454c3a","tid":584720,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}